snippet.title: OpenMinded Teaser
snippet.description:
Teaser for upcoming OpenMinded game. A cinematic horror adventure game. Follow us on Instagram and twitter to watch us create this game from sketch to game. Thanks for your support! We would love to here from you!

Follow our development and help us beta test our games!
